colss=list(data.columns)
colss.pop(0)
for m in colss:
    fig,axs=plt.subplots(2,2)
    count=1
    for i,j,k in zip(range(0,22,7),[[0,0],[0,1],[1,0],[1,1]],["blue","red","orange","green"]):
        count+=1
        a="tab"+":"+k
        
        if(count==5):
            x=datajne["Date_tmp"][i:i+7+2]
            y=datajne[m][i:i+7+2]
            

        else:
        
            x=datajne["Date_tmp"][i:i+7]
            y=datajne[m][i:i+7]
        if(count<4):
                axs[j[0],j[1]].set_title(m)
        axs[j[0],j[1]].plot(x,y,a)
        axs[j[0],j[1]].fill_between(x,0,y,color=k)

new_cols=["Daily_Confirmed_Diff","Total_Confirmed_Diff","Daily_Recovered_Diff","Total_Recovered_Diff","Daily_Deceased_Diff","Total_Deceased_diff"]
existing_cols=list(datajne_diff.columns)
existing_cols.pop(0)
existing_cols
prv_vals=[8789,190649,4928,91862,222,5406]
for i,j,l in zip(new_cols,existing_cols,prv_vals):
    datajne_diff[i]=list(range(len(datajne_diff)))
    datajne_diff[i][0]=datajne_diff[j][0]-l
    for k in range(0,len(datajne_diff)-1):
        datajne_diff[i][k+1]=datajne_diff[j][k+1]-datajne_diff[j][k]

kys=["daily_cnf_diff_pos_neg","total_cnf_diff_pos_neg","daily_rcvd_diff_pos_neg","total_rcvd_diff_pos_neg","daily_dcsd_diff_pos_neg","total_dcsd_diff_pos_neg"]
new_cols=["Daily_Confirmed_Diff","Total_Confirmed_Diff","Daily_Recovered_Diff","Total_Recovered_Diff","Daily_Deceased_Diff","Total_Deceased_diff"]
pos_neg_dict={}
pos_neg_len_dict={}
a=[]
b=[]
for i,j in zip(kys,new_cols):
    pos=datajne_diff[datajne_diff[j]>0]
    a.append(pos)
    b.append(len(pos))
    neg=datajne_diff[datajne_diff[j]<0]
    a.append(neg)
    b.append(len(neg))
    zro=datajne_diff[datajne_diff[j]==0]
    a.append(zro)
    b.append(len(zro))
    pos_neg_dict.update({i:a})
    pos_neg_len_dict.update({i:b})
    a=[]
    b=[]

new_cols=["Daily_Confirmed_Ratio","Total_Confirmed_Ratio","Daily_Recovered_Ratio","Total_Recovered_Ratio","Daily_Deceased_Ratio","Total_Deceased_Ratio"]
existing_cols=list(datajne_ratio.columns)
existing_cols.pop(0)
existing_cols
prv_vals=[8789,190649,4928,91862,222,5406]
for i,j,l in zip(new_cols,existing_cols,prv_vals):
    datajne_ratio[i]=list(range(len(datajne_ratio)))
    datajne_ratio[i][0]=round(datajne_ratio[j][0]/l,2)
    tmp=[]
    tmp.append(datajne_ratio[i][0])
    for k in range(0,len(datajne_ratio)-1):
        tmp.append(round(datajne_ratio[j][k+1]/datajne_ratio[j][k],2))
    datajne_ratio[i]=tmp
datajne_ratio.head()
